    • Constructor Detail

      • ServiceRequest

        public ServiceRequest(String document,
              SupportedMimeType type)
        Construct a request for the online service to annotate or classify a document provided as part of the request.
        Parameters:
        document - the content to process.
        type - the MIME type that the service should use to parse the document.

      • ServiceRequest

        public ServiceRequest(URL documentUrl,
              SupportedMimeType type)
        Construct a request for the online service to annotate or classify a document downloaded directly from a remote URL.
        Parameters:
        documentUrl - the URL from which the document should be downloaded. This must be accessible to the service so it must not require authentication credentials etc. (but it may be, for example, a pre-signed Amazon S3 URL).
        type - the MIME type that the service should use to parse the document.
